data.description: Beautiful 3/3 and half bath home in the North Georgia Mountains. Convieniently located between Dawsonville and Dahlonega. Large master overlooking fenced in back yard. Large living/family room with rock fireplace. Spacious kitchen with island. Home features beautiful hardwood floors, tile and carpet. Full unfinished basement on .59 acre in Castleberry Ridge with tennis / swimming. Lots of room and Mountain Views.
